text: Circumcincta est hec terra his terminibus<../images/tbar.gif>is þonne ærest from wifeles lace<../images/tbar.gif>swa up andlang riðiges<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to fagan floran & þonne swa andlang slædes be þam twam lytlan beorgan<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to wulfunes treow stealle will.

An suna<../images/tbar.gif>swa þwyres ofer<../images/tbar.gif>furlang<../images/tbar.gif>on þa þyrnan westewarde þær se mycla þorn stod<../images/tbar.gif>swa on fugelmere<../images/tbar.gif>þonne a ondlang dices oð<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymeð to horwyllan<../images/tbar.gif>swa ondlang riðies<../images/tbar.gif>hit cymð to cearwyllan þonne mæreð hit cerwelle seoððan.
